content.html: This week: how to buy a house! Yes one of us bought one (BUT WHO) (tessa) and she tells us what she learned. Namely you can’t just keep yelling “BUT IM GOOD FOR IT” at the bank. Listen here: podcasts.apple.com/gb/podcast/how…
